{"tid":89043,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[SPLIT]  思。裂  集中討論區 (有劇透成分)","createTime":"2017-01-21T05:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T15:38:22.000Z","uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebdaefae098fef467e84ea9165192ce797ceebd2","tid":89043,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完依套 覺得男主角真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一睇到佢 好熟面口 但係睇晒成套都重係醒唔起佢係乜水 <br />\n最後睇番poster 先記得原來係Xmen既Professor <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw睇住佢最主要果幾個人格 <br />\nBarry - 民主型領袖？可惜出場無耐就被囚禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\nHedvit - 點解9歲既佢 有能力搶燈見光 又可以囚禁住Barry? <br />\n<br />\nDennis - 保護主義 一直都覺得佢好偏激 唔聽人講 但後來又比 Dr. Feltcher說服到 (點知最後Beast都係出左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\nPatricia - 女版温柔化Dennis?  同Dennis,  Hedwig組成左部落 但係冇乜作用咁<br />\n<br />\n雖然係改編自 24個比利  但電影版睇到最後1個身份既時候 都估唔到會咁天馬行空<br />\n等我重以為Dennis同Dr. Fletcher坦白既時候係鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係新聞報道 我都唔知Beast真係Beast(動物合成體)<br />\n<br />\nbtw男主角超級好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會覺得佢係到扮緊23個人<br />\n而真係有個feel係果個身份出左黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過電影時間問題 只係睇到主要果幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   但係都值得一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66352a304d7cf91b1b82cc9ec9f10369460051f","tid":89043,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012f0e083680ad05d1f3aea44be7bbd27c164524","tid":89043,"uid":70280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T06:34:12.000Z","msg":"留名睇anya taylor-joy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/to